pageContext.claim: “I can't get any -- we can't get any votes from the Democrats. We can't get any votes.”
pageContext.analysis: This is false. Democrats do not support all of Trump’s proposals, but that doesn't mean initiatives he supports haven’t garnered Democratic votes. Sen. Kirsten Sinema (D-Ariz.) has voted in line with Trump’s position %4.4 percent of the time, according to FiveThirtyEight.
